# Text Shortener

## Description
A skill that turns long text into short, clear bullet points. The skill condenses information into 2-3 concise bullet points while keeping the key meaning intact, using professional language without extra commentary.

## Trigger Conditions
- Automatically activates when user requests text summarization or bullet points
- Responds to phrases like "summarize this", "create bullets", "shorten this", "key points", "main points"
- Available when user submits long text that needs condensing

## Functionality
- Converts long text into 2-3 clear bullet points
- Preserves key meaning and important information
- Uses professional language throughout
- Adds no extra commentary beyond the essential points
- Creates concise, scannable summaries
- Maintains the core message of the original text

## Usage Examples
- "Summarize this into bullet points"
- "Create 3 bullet points from this text"
- "Shorten this into key points"
- "What are the main points here?"
- "Turn this into bullets"

## Parameters
- Input: Long text that needs to be shortened
- Output: 2-3 concise bullet points with key information

## Constraints
- Output must be 2-3 bullet points maximum
- Language must remain professional
- No extra commentary or explanations beyond the bullets
- Key meaning from original text must be preserved
- Points should be concise and scannable
